te to call them off — and here... this horror. 'Luzhin,' she cried, 'people will be here any minute. I don't know what to do.... Say something to me.

Perhaps you've had an accident, perhaps you met an unpleasant acquaintance? Tell me. I beg you, I can't beg any more...'

And suddenly Luzhin stopped. It was as if the whole world had stopped. It happened in the drawing room, by the phonograph.

'Full stop,' she said softly and burst into tears. Luzhin began to take things out of his pockets —